Company Overview of Sound Shore Fund, Inc



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Sound Shore Fund, Inc is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Sound Shore Management, Inc. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in value stocks of large-cap and mid-cap companies. It employs fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach focusing on factors like low absolute and relative P/E valuations to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index. Sound Shore Fund, Inc was formed on May 17, 1985 and is domiciled in the United States.


8 Sound Shore DriveSuite 180Greenwich, CT 06830-7242United StatesFounded in 1985



